<p class="has-white-color has-text-color">The <em>Love, Scarborough</em> campaign is helping us rise to new heights. Our hospitals have always faced an uphill climb, but together, we’re rising higher to ensure every patient receives the care they deserve. Donations help us continue providing exceptional care while upgrading our facilities and investing in cutting-edge equipment.</p>



