<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Visiting a patient? Remember to <em>first</em> check in with the Unit Clerk or team</h2>



<p>When you get to patient unit,&nbsp;check in with the Unit Clerk about any important information. You may be required to put on additional Personal Protective Equipment.</p>



<div class="wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex">
